<meta name="Keywords" content="Alfred Russell Wallace, Alfred R. Wallace, Alfred Russel Wallace Page, Alfred Russel Wallace, A. R. Wallace, natural selection, God, Claparede, life, Charles H. Smith, consciousness, protoplasm, Contributions to the Theory of Natural Selection, evolution" />

